Source documents
----------------------------------------------------------------
This compilation contains and links to clinical-trial protocol PDFs
that are themselves works of their respective sponsors (Pfizer/BioNTech,
ModernaTX, AstraZeneca, Janssen / Johnson & Johnson). Each source PDF
is reproduced or linked under its original terms — typically as a
FOIA-released public record (PHMPT.org), a clinicaltrials.gov filing,
a journal-publication supplement (NEJM), or an Internet Archive copy.
The CC BY 4.0 license applies to this site's compilation, extraction,
and presentation of those records; the underlying protocol documents
remain works of their respective sponsors.
